    <title>「计算机系统」课程作业_四</title>
    <url>/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>《深入理解计算机系统》，<em>第五章：优化程序性能</em> 和<em>第六章：存储器层次结构</em> 的部分作业</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="深入理解计算机系统（2版）5-17">深入理解计算机系统（2版）5.17</h2>
<p><img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193238835.png" alt="image-20220516193238835"><img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193318663.png" alt="image-20220516193318663"></p>
<blockquote>
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193408307.png" class title="image-20220516193408307">
</blockquote>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">inner_517</span><span class="params">(vec_ptr x, vec_ptr y, <span class="type">data_t</span> *dest)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> i, length=<span class="built_in">vec_length</span>(x);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> limit=length<span class="number">-2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">data_t</span> *xdata, *ydata, sum0=<span class="number">0</span>, sum1=<span class="number">0</span>, sum2=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    xdata=<span class="built_in">get_vec_start</span>(x);</span><br><span class="line">    ydata=<span class="built_in">get_vec_start</span>(y);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//三路并行相加</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="number">0</span>; i&lt;limit; i+=<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sum0+=xdata[i]*ydata[i];</span><br><span class="line">        sum1+=xdata[i+<span class="number">1</span>]*ydata[i+<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        sum2+=xdata[i+<span class="number">2</span>]*ydata[i+<span class="number">2</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(i&lt;length)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sum0+=xdata[i]*ydata[i];</span><br><span class="line">        i++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    *dest=sum0+sum1+sum2;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>A</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>每个结点都起码需要用两个寄存器来存储和操作，但一个时钟周期只能给一个寄存器加载一个值</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>B</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>在 IA32 上寄存器的数量不够多</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="深入理解计算机系统（2版）5-19">深入理解计算机系统（2版）5.19</h2>
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193441059.png" class title="image-20220516193441059">
<hr>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> *<span class="title">basic_memset</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">void</span> *s, <span class="type">int</span> c, <span class="type">size_t</span> n)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> word=<span class="number">0</span>, *slong, cnt=<span class="number">0</span>, i;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> *schar;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n&lt;<span class="number">3</span>*<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(word)) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">basic_memset</span>(s, c, n);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(i=<span class="number">0</span>; i&lt;<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(word); i++) word=(word&lt;&lt;<span class="number">8</span>)|(c&amp;<span class="number">0xff</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        schar=s;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(schar%<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(word)!=<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            *schar++=c;</span><br><span class="line">            cnt++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    slong=schar;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(cnt&lt;n<span class="number">-2</span>*<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(word)+<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        *slong=word;</span><br><span class="line">        cnt+=<span class="number">2</span>*<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(word);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="同上，6-42-6-44">同上，6.42+6.44</h2>
<p><img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193510091.png" alt="image-20220516193510091"><img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193523815.png" alt="image-20220516193523815"></p>
<hr>
<p>每个 <code>pixel</code> 结构体里面四个 <code>char</code> ，总共占四个字节，所以一个结构体刚好占高速缓存的一行。代码是遍历这个结构体，因此每次就是 miss hit hit hit。</p>
<p><strong>不命中率为25%</strong>。</p>
<hr>
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516193549343.png" class title="image-20220516193549343">
<hr>
<p>每次都把相邻的四个字节的结构体赋值为0，所以<strong>不命中率是100%</strong></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="参考答案">参考答案</h2>
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516200530945.png" class title="image-20220516200530945">
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516203004223.png" class title="image-20220516203004223">
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516205953898.png" class title="image-20220516205953898">
<img src="/2022/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/05/16/%E3%80%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%8D%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A-%E5%9B%9B/image-20220516210008192.png" class title="image-20220516210008192">
